Norilsk May Seek to Acquire Metalloinvest, Vedomosti Reports

-- B y   H e n r y   M e y e r
-- 
2011-04-07T16:58:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/norilsk-may-seek-to-acquire-metalloinvest-vedomosti-reports.html
OAO GMK Norilsk Nickel,  Russia ’s
largest mining company, may seek to acquire billionaire Alisher Usmanov’s Metalloinvest holding company, Vedomosti reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Vladimir Strzhalkovsky.  Such an acquisition would be part of a strategy for
Norilsk’s expansion, Strzhalkovsky was cited as saying by the
Moscow-based newspaper.  A spokesperson for Usmanov, who asked not to be identified,
declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henry Meyer in Moscow at 
 hmeyer4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Amanda Jordan at   ajordan11@bloomberg.net  